commit.message: Version 1.4.0
doc/install: work around tools not knowing \testexamplefalse

doc: change make_doc to abort when there are errors

Also use "rm -rf" to delete the ../htm dir, in case it does not yet exist.
doc: adjust to 'new' name of GAP's bib file (since GAP 4.5)
Add .gitignore

lib/Autom.g*: save found generators in component instead of attribute

There was no good reason to use an attribute.

lib/Autom.g*: save states in component instead of attribute

This saves time and space by avoiding unnecessarily and unintendedly
copying the list of states and thereby the whole automaton.
This was detected while contemplating
 https://github.com/gap-system/gap/issues/1522

Switch testall.g to use TestDirectory

This has the advantage that the tests produce an exit code indicating the
status of the tests, and also uniform defined output, both of which we can be
checked in an automated fashion for the GAP distribution.
Added source repository and issue tracker to PackageInfo.g
doc/make_doc: avoid keeping old parts of HTML documentation
Version 1.3.1

/lib/Whitehd.gi: use NC version of GroupHomomorphismByImages

In the last case, this is needed to avoid a non-terminating check
introduced with commit gap-system/gap@ad260e7 which appears in
GAP 4.8.2.
doc/FGA.tex: fix examples
lib/ExtAutom.gi: avoid swapping variables when it's not needed

lib/ReprAct.gi: perform undo in reverse order

Does the same, but is easier to reason about.
lib/Hom.gi: use NC version of Subgroup
Fix handling of homs with trivial range / source
Version 1.3.0

lib/ReprAct.gi: fix bug in RepresentativeActionOp

Fix a bug reportet by Ignat Soroko,
see test case added in commit 8d535ae1.

RepresentativeActionOp(f,g,h) would return x even if
g^x was only a proper subset of h, as long as g and h had the same rank and
(after cyclic reduction) the same number of important cosets.
tst/FGA.tst: Add test for bug reportet by Ignat Soroko
Update tst/FGA.tst
Add package (tarball) creation script
In doc/* replace ../../.. with GAPROOT which should be a link.
Version 1.2.0
Get rid of CVS keyword $Id$.

Finally fix bug #122 reported by Laurent Bartholdi.
Also improved a related case and added a test case.
Fixed typo in comment reported by Max Horn

Added \in-method for automorphism groups of free groups contributed by Max Horn.

This allows using Image with the result of IsomorphismFpGroup
applied to the automorphism group of a free group;
changed documentation accordingly.
Version 1.1.1
cleanup (unused variable)
